data.description: Wonderful setting in the country with a cozy one level ranch on 6.74 acres. This well-maintained home is the perfect blend of comfort & functionality. The welcoming living room and spacious bonus room, both have pellet stoves to keep you cozy on those chilly nights. The kitchen features modern appliances & vinyl plank floors. The primary suite has a private access to a covered deck, where you can enjoy your morning coffee. Need outbuildings and room for recreational toys? You?ll find a shed for all your garden tools. There's also a greenhouse, small barn, 48 x 30 pole barn, perfect for all your storage needs. The property provides room for parking all your toys and RVs. From the large covered deck, you?ll enjoy the wonderful pastural view of the flat, useable acreage that?s ideal for raising animals or farming. Conveniently located amongst the Amity Hills in Wine Country, with easy access to McMinnville and Salem.
